{"tid":1458741,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好圍爐打飛機住！大家唔好圍爐打飛機住！大家唔好圍爐打飛機住！","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T15:10:43.000Z","uid":147785,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"49532194cc2f11bb9f8db4805e762de785f0c79e","tid":1458741,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:52:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">今日仲未完 唔好階段性勝利就掉以輕心</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有幾個問題 希望集思廣益</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. <span style=\"color: red;\">到底聽日係咪重入機場 點解唔見有宣傳?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 今日D狗無得名正言順殺入機場 係因為無發生任何暴力/破壞事件</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇諗過如果D臥底主動造成破壞 點應對?</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">民陣決定818搞和理非遊行</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">依家機場牌初嚐勝果</span> 我相信依家大風向係 <span style=\"color: violet;\">和理非搞機場至 10.1 因為對家明顯想係10.1之前平息件事</span> 但我地依段時間 逢集會/遊行必定會同班狗衝突 加上臥底問題未有解決辦法 <br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果有共識依段時間 應避免同狗發生衝突 直至10.1  喺818時點樣令所有前線都有呢個共識?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n聽日入機場記得帶gip!!!!!"},{"pid":"1e5d9d926a9ff98a2ef46fb0beb820762f6dd4f8","tid":1458741,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:53:48.000Z","msg":"[賽後檢討] 抗爭者進化史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1458526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1458526</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a1b5928ccbcb05a5d6b1b4994987c6ebf9901a67","tid":1458741,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:55:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8.13 1pm 再入機場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style